name: Supercell: a video game with a unique blend of strategy and racing for Windows & Mac
blurb: Supercell is a unique hybrid game, combining strategical puzzle-solving with fast cars. Use your quick wit and racing finesse to set the fastest time.

rewards.reward: With this pledge, you will gain the satisfaction of knowing you helped, and also receive exclusive updates about the project. As a bonus, your name will be listed as a contributor in the credits of the game and on the website.
You will receive the above prize, plus a free download of the game when it is released!

Receive all of the above, plus get continued access to the newest and greatest version of the game until beta testing. Once funding is over, access will be limited for the general public to a small demo; but you will get exclusive access to a continually updated version of the game.

At this level, you will get all of the above, plus the full color, packaged, physical version of the game, delivered right to your door! (add $5 more dollars if mailing address is outside the 48 contiguous states)
Get everything from above, plus a sweet Supercell graphic t-shirt! (add $5 more dollars if mailing address is outside the 48 contiguous states)

First, you get everything from above...but here's where it gets interesting: not only will you get access to the project through its entire development, you will be a beta tester! You will try the latest features, find bugs, and give your input. Your name will be listed in the credits as a beta tester in the game and on the website.
Receive everything from above, plus limited run, full color prints of the vehicles from the game (add $5 more dollars if mailing address is outside the 48 contiguous states).

Here's an awesome level...not only will you get everything from above, but you will also receive a special edition version of the game. This includes the physical copy of the game, plus a special Supercell racing wheel with pedals! You will also get a second exclusive Supercell t-shirt not available anywhere else (add $10 more dollars if mailing address is outside the 48 contiguous states).

Last, but not least, is the $500 level...so what do you get? First, you will get not one, but two of everything from above! You will get two downloads of the game, two physical copies of the game (one with alternate artwork), the regular prints of the vehicles plus a second set of exclusive vehicle prints, and the regular and limited edition t-shirts. This only includes one steering wheel and pedals set. Whew! That's quite a lot, but there is one more thing...your name will be listed in the game and on the website as an executive producer. Imagine your permanent and personal stamp on the game for all to see! (add $20 more dollars if mailing address is outside the 48 contiguous states)
